title: Leading fast food restaurants in the United Kingdom 2015
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Share of respondents for 19 number of Responses.
The Share of respondents is appeared to be the highest at Response McDonald's and lowest at Response Prefer not to say.
The Share of respondents of Response McDonald's is 57.0% larger than the minimum value at Prefer not to say.
min_summary: This bar chart has 19 columns on the x axis representing Response, and Share of respondents in each Response on the y axis.

max_summary: This is a bar chart representing Response in the x axis and Share of respondents in the y axis.
The Share of respondents is appeared to be the highest at Response McDonald's and lowest at Response Prefer not to say.
Second maximum Share of respondents is found at Response KFC.
